{
  "texts": [
    "ML systems in lung disease diagnosis benefit from regular validation based on real-world clinical results [10][11][12].",
    "• This review analyzes ML approaches for diagnosing lung diseases.",
    "The main contribution of the research is: • It investigates and addresses prominent lung diseases such as pneumonia, lung cancer, and COVID-19.",
    "• It investigates and addresses the publicly accessible imaging modalities datasets for each prominent lung disease.",
    "• It explores and addresses existing challenges and issues in diagnosing prominent lung diseases using ML and its associated novel solutions."
  ]
}